data.description:
Beautifully remodeled 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home, where modern living meets convenience. Step inside to discover a fully renovated interior that boasts both style and functionality featuring an updated kitchen, appliances, flooring, bathrooms and a brand new AC unit. 
Outside your front door, you'll find a vibrant community that offers more than just a home. A sparkling community pool awaits your leisurely afternoons, while a playground and basketball court are perfect for active kids and families.
Experience the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this low-maintenance gem. Make it your haven today!
